text: Adebisi is both a surname and a given name of Yoruba origin, meaning "the king/crown/royalty produced more". Notable people with the name include: *Ade Adebisi (born 1986), Nigerian-born rugby league player *Mola Adebisi (born 1973), German television presenter and actor *Adebisi Akande, Nigerian politician Fictional characters: *Simon Adebisi, character in the television series Oz ==References== Category:Yoruba given names Category:Yoruba-language surnames
